ores cognition, memory, perception, and neurological disorders at molecular, cellular, and systems levels."], "scores": [0.7923197869901202, 0.7784005143507529, 0.6365491267238393, 0.5790183014999992, 0.5619853074529279], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Astrophysics", "Astronomy", "Meteorology", "Geology", "Neuroscience"]}}